Dependencias que instalamos: 
	npm install bootstrap --save
	npm install jquery --save
	npm install popper.js --save
	npm install lite-server --save--dev

El flag --save se agrega ya que luego serána utilizadas en producción

Agregamos el script a package.json:
	 "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
    "dev": "lite-server"
  },

Corremos el servidor con:
	npm run dev

Vinculamos el index.html con los:
	css de bootstrap (bootstrap.min.css) 
	con los archivos de js

Que sacamos de node_modules

 	<!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap-grid.css" />

    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
 	<script src="node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="node_modules/popper.js/dist/popper-utils.min.js"></script>
    <script src="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="public/css/style.css" />
    <title>Hello, world!</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="node_modules/popper.js/dist/popper-utils.min.js"></script>
    <script src="node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
